episodes.title: BoJack Horseman Christmas Special: Sabrina's Christmas Wish
episodes.plot: BoJack and Todd watch a very special Christmas episode of "Horsin' Around" to celebrate the holidays.

episodes.title: Brand New Couch
episodes.plot: Picking up where he left off, Bojack Horseman is now set to start filming his dream movie Secretariat.

episodes.title: Yesterdayland
episodes.plot: BoJack is drawn to the one female in town who has no idea who he is (because she was in a coma). Todd opens a theme park.

episodes.title: Still Broken
episodes.plot: A funeral turns into a treasure hunt for the "Horsin' Around" cast and a potential schmoozefest for Princess Carolyn and Mr. Peanutbutter. Meanwhile, Todd briefly reinvents himself.

episodes.title: After the Party
episodes.plot: Mr. Peanutbutter throws Diane a surprise birthday party, putting tension on their relationship. Princess Carolyn and Vincent have a serious talk. Wanda tells BoJack a joke.

episodes.title: Chickens
episodes.plot: Todd tries to save a chicken from the slaughter house while Bojack and Kelsey are allowed some bonding time.

episodes.title: Higher Love
episodes.plot: Princess Carolyn sees an opportunity when Mr. Peanutbutter's agent dies. BoJack flips when he says the "L" word out loud to Wanda.

episodes.title: Hank After Dark
episodes.plot: Diane goes off script during BoJack's book tour, jeopardizing Mr. Peanutbutter's new show. Todd gets involved in international affairs.

episodes.title: Let's Find Out
episodes.plot: BoJack Horseman is a contestant on Mr. Peanutbutter's new game show, facing off against a mystery 'bigger celebrity' contestant.

episodes.title: The Shot
episodes.plot: BoJack, Kelsey, Todd, Princess Carolyn, and Mr. Peanutbutter attempt to shoot a crucial scene in the Secretariat movie that was not in the script. Princess Carolyn and Diane contemplate their respective careers.

episodes.title: Yes And
episodes.plot: Diane crashes at BoJack's place after quitting her job following Sebastian St. Clair, which puts a strain on BoJack and Wanda's relationship. Todd joins an improv comedy troupe which turns out to be a cult.

episodes.title: Escape from L.A.
episodes.plot: Bojack runs off to New Mexico to reconnect with an old friend, only to find she's happily married with a family. After staying longer than planned, Bojack makes another life mistake.

episodes.title: Out to Sea
episodes.plot: BoJack discovers the Secretariat film was finished without him. Princess Carolyn starts her own agency firm. Todd finds himself trapped in the improv comedy cult.
